snippet.title: AJ TRIP
snippet.description:
My Channel will contain these types of videos. Reaction videos like you see all over YouTube. Rapid Reactions where I live stream after an event I feel worthy enough to do so. Top 10 lists where I rank the top 10 of something. "The Word According To Me" videos where I talk or rant about something on my mind. And much more.

Topics includes anything from sports to politics to pop culture. Although there will be a lot of sports and wrestling just to let you know. 

Please subscribe and join me on my quest to make great content for you to hopefully enjoy.

If you like what you see and want to support me, become a patron
https://www.patreon.com/AJTRIP, 

OR
You want to give a tip/donation go here:
https://www.paypal.com/cgi-bin/webscr?c

Also, I have a back-up channel where if this channel goes down, you can find me there. Also if you love gaming my gaming videos from Twitch will be there as well.'
My back-up channel
YOUTUBE BACK-UP: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCvP2rLLDnHozh7nnL_0nmlQ
